title: Snake God, The, Il Dio Serpente 1970 Nadia Cassini, Beryl Cunningham, Juana Sobreda, Koike Mahoco, Sergio Tramonti + Piero Vivarelli

sources.title: Snake God, The, Il Dio Serpente 1970 Nadia Cassini, Beryl Cunningham, Juana Sobreda, Koike Mahoco, Sergio Tramonti + Piero Vivarelli
sources.description: A relic from the days when European film makers would convince their backers to pay for trips to exotic locales. In this case Piero Vivarelli got to go to Venezuela and Colombia to film this odd movie about a love god who appears in the form of a snake. Audio is Italian with English subtitles available.
